<p class="ql-align-justify">上海大酒店四楼上海厅</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">（上海市黄浦区九江路505号）</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">议程安排</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>致辞\推介环节</strong></p>
